title: Sigur Rós "Hrafntinna" : Converse EMPTY SPACE #4
description:
EMPTY SPACE is a brand new music video series from Converse and La Blogotheque that showcases a wide range of artists playing in empty venues across Paris. The quintessentially French establishments provide the perfect setting for intimate, unexpected and powerful moments that allow their music to shine.

Track: Hrafntinna by Sigur Rós
